@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@alexToken = course-alex-local-token
@rileyToken = course-riley-local-token

### Reset, seed two tenants, and index tenant-tagged evidence
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/reset

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/seed

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/index

### Missing verified identity is rejected
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/articles

### Alex sees Tenant Blue evidence; spoofed headers are ignored
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/search?q=How%20do%20I%20restore%20VPN%20access%20and%20refresh%20my%20certificate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
X-User-Id: customer-riley
X-Tenant-Id: tenant-red

### Riley sees Tenant Red evidence and never the restricted payroll record
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/search?q=How%20do%20I%20restore%20VPN%20access%20and%20enroll%20my%20replacement%20device
Authorization: Bearer {{rileyToken}}

### This explicit cross-tenant target is denied before confirmation state is created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Escalate ticket T-2002",
  "conversationId": "course-cross-tenant"
}

### App-owned intake redacts before both database storage and vector indexing
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Contact alex.private@example.com about SSN 123-45-6789"
}

### Only the redacted projection can be loaded
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/support/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}

### Readiness exposes enabled boundaries and vector counts, not credentials
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/readiness
